flowchart LR
  U[Web / API Clients] --> CDN[CDN + WAF]
  CDN --> GW[API Gateway<br/>rate limit, auth, routing]
  GW --> LB[Layer 7 Load Balancer]
  LB --> APP[FastAPI / BFF Cluster]
  APP --> ORCH[Agent Orchestrator]
  ORCH --> TOOLS[Tool Sandbox<br/>SQL, Python, charting]
  ORCH --> RETR[Retrieval Service]
  ORCH --> LLM[LLM Serving Pool<br/>Qwen fine-tuned + fallback APIs]
  RETR --> VDB[(Vector DB)]
  RETR --> OBJ[(Object Storage<br/>uploads, reports)]
  APP --> CACHE[(Redis Cluster<br/>sessions, queues, hot cache)]
  APP --> DB[(PostgreSQL / MySQL<br/>users, billing, projects)]
  APP --> MQ[Kafka / Pulsar]
  MQ --> WORKER[Async Workers<br/>ETL, long jobs, exports]
  WORKER --> OBJ
  WORKER --> DB
  LLM --> GPU[GPU Inference Nodes<br/>vLLM/TensorRT-LLM]
  APP --> OBS[Observability<br/>Prometheus, Grafana, ELK, tracing]
  LLM --> OBS
  WORKER --> OBS
  SEC[Security / Governance<br/>PII masking, audit, policy] --> APP
  SEC --> TOOLS

